summaries.short: In an effort to dig up dirt on Abaddonn's CEO, Amy, Tyler and Dougie try to befriend his assistant Eileen.
summaries.full: In an effort to dig up dirt on Szidon, Amy, Tyler and Dougie (still irate over being betrayed by management) take turns trying to befriend the CEO's assistant, Eileen. Eventually agreeing to join the trio for drinks after work, Eileen takes a shine to Tyler, who ends up with a guilty conscience when the two start dating.

summaries.short: Amy daydreams about building a relationship with Jeff after the two find gold in Szidon's personal emails.
summaries.full: In the giddy afterglow of finding gold in Szidon's personal emails, Amy lets down her guard with Jeff, and indulges herself in daydreams of building a perfect life with the dashing journalist. The dream comes to an abrupt end, however, when Levi unexpectedly returns from rehab in Hawaii.

summaries.short: Amy gets inspired by social media; Dougie has second thoughts about reporting the security breach to HR.
summaries.full: Amy becomes inspired to use social media to spread her message of change, and attends a gathering of liberal intellectuals on Jeff's invitation. Dougie learns who hacked into Abaddonn's system, but has second thoughts about reporting the breach to HR. Amy has a chance run-in with Abaddonn CEO Charles Szidon.

summaries.short: Amy gets an unexpected meeting with Charles Szidon; Dougie goes off the rails.
summaries.full: In hopes she will drop her crusade against Abaddonn, Tyler gets Eileen to arrange a meeting for Amy with Szidon, who turns out to have more compassion than Amy expected. Dougie goes off the rails after getting official word about Cogentiva's future. Amy confides in Krista about the Abaddonn expose, and has a tense meeting with Levi.

summaries.short: Season Two Finale. On the precipice of bringing down Abaddonn, Amy prepares herself and those around her for the inevitable fallout.
summaries.full: Season Two Finale. On the precipice of bringing down Abaddonn, Amy warns Tyler to prepare himself for the inevitable fallout. When Szidon gets wind of her intentions, Amy wrongly points a finger at Krista, who has just given birth. As the crisis reaches its denouement, Amy is intercepted by HR, who take her to meet with Szidon and Abaddonn lawyers for a final reckoning.

summaries.short: Tyler scrambles to find a scapegoat after Amy's breach of security is exposed.
summaries.full: Amy and a still-reluctant Tyler meet Jeff at an LA jazz club, where Jeff reveals he's already been working on a story about Abaddonn but needs proof of bribery--leading Amy to revel in her revenge fantasies. Later, Abaddonn's breach of security is exposed--leaving Tyler scrambling to find a solution that won't lead investigators to him or Amy.
